INSERT INTO `tickets` VALUES (1,'2025-03-21 07:32:46.000000','Get Business course help from our community','NO-REPLY','[ The Coursera community can help if you get stuck or need career advice - Coursera ]  If you get stuck or want career advice the Coursera Community is here for you Congratulations on getting started on a course from our Business catalog, you’ve already taken the hardest step! I’m reaching out to make sure you’ve heard about our community  . Thousands of learners like you use the community every day to: * Get help when they’re stuck. * Get advice on the right career path and courses for them. * Meet people with the same interests or on the same journey Our community includes educators, seasoned professionals and Community Guides dedicated to helping out, so the majority of questions get answered within a few days. You can use the Business topic  to ask questions and learn more about Business, or join one or more groups  to find people like you. Start by introducing yourself or, if you’re not ready to post just yet, follow the topics and groups you’re interested in so you can come back to the conversations later. Don\'t learn alone! Visit the Community  [Coursera]  [App Store]  [Android]  [FB]  [Twitter]  [Insta]  [LI]  Help  | Coursera for Business  | Privacy Notice  | Unsubscribe  © 2025 Coursera Inc. All rights reserved. Coursera and the Coursera logo are registered trademarks of Coursera, Inc. All other trademarks are property of their respective owners. Log in to manage all your notification preferences in Email Settings  . Coursera | 2440 West El Camino Real, Suite 500, Mountain View, CA 94040 USA','no-reply@m.mail.coursera.org','EMAIL','CLOSED','TKT-1769592827785','Rahul Sharma (NET)','Application Support Team','SOFTWARE','2026-01-28 13:30:24.645122',0.9,_binary '','MEDIUM','CRASH','AI','2026-01-29 06:54:17.870837','2026-01-29 04:40:06.953043','SLA Breach - Level 3 - Department Head escalation. Priority: MEDIUM, SLA: 8 hours, Overtime: 7525.1