ach - Level 3 - Department Head escalation. Priority: HIGH, SLA: 4 hours, Overtime: 8741.4 hours (218735% of SLA)',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,2,'LEVEL_3','2026-04-02 17:36:33.688149','Priya Singh (NET)','2026-01-29 04:40:29.115841',_binary '','2025-04-01 05:15:03.000000',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(3,'2025-04-23 05:07:48.000000','May 2025 NPTEL Exams - Hall Tickets Released!','ONLINECOURSES','***THIS ANNOUNCEMENT IS ONLY FOR THOSE WHO HAVE REGISTERED AND PAID FOR THE MAY 2025 EXAM***Dear Candidate,Your Hall Ticket / admit card for the NPTEL Exam(s) in May, 2025 has been released.You may have received an email with a link to download the Hall ticket to your registered email ID. Please refer to it for further details.It is the responsibility of the candidate to download the hall ticket at their end.&nbsp;Please check your registered email ID.Note:&nbsp;Requests for changes in exam city, exam center, exam date, session, or course will NOT be entertained.Please write to&nbsp;support@nptel.iitm.ac.in&nbsp;for any further queries.All the best for your exams!With Regards,NPTEL Team  --  You received this message because you are subscribed to the Google Groups &quot;Announcement list for Programming In Java&quot; group. To unsubscribe from this group and stop receiving emails from it, send an email to noc25-cs57-announce+unsubscribe@nptel.iitm.ac.in. To view this discussion visit https://groups.google.com/a/nptel.iitm.ac.in/d/msgid/noc25-cs57-announce/roGqLpZYSfCjCxGZIhiicA%40geopod-ismtpd-0. For more options, visit https://groups.google.com/a/nptel.iitm.ac.in/d/optout.','onlinecourses@nptel.iitm.ac.in','EMAIL','CLOSED','TKT-1769592989331','Sneha Patel (APP)','Email Support Team','EMAIL','2026-01-28 13:30:24.685612',0.9,_binary '','MEDIUM','EMAIL_SEND','AI','2026-02-07 10:19:34.009436','2026-01-29 04:40:51.015462','SLA Breach - Level 3 - Department Head escalation. Priority: MEDIUM, SLA: 8 hours, Overtime: 6735.6 hours (84294% of SLA)',NULL,'Groups &quot;Annou