, and then some. Also ICYMI, here’s “What’s new in Bolt v2”! Hey builders, This week we’re focusing on how to take your site from simple to stunning (and making sure you’re making the most of Bolt v2). Is your site looking too “starter project”? Join us tomorrow (https://d5llC804.na1.hubspotlinks.com/Ctc/DQ+113/d5llC804/VWxdHS4xy-PzW7kM6n98JTlVRW3X6sTS5DF8KNN6WXHYv5fr76W50kH_H6lZ3kwW2RPjjX4WBDFNW8-h6665QGg1VN3sTN_bZWH0PW2P-GPR6wdxp9W3xk4pc89JX_kW1C9Xfr9ckw3HW30L75B6zzQm_W2zV2nw8W9jd7VZ2S7c9gBYyBW1KzNWd5hvk5SN4nYLXMK62fqW6Y8_sM3tyjjrW3gJdhM4CxvFKW1S1ZKQ4TZ8MCV3fwjK26sGT6N7b9xB5J7fHvW3JY85f93Rm8PN3zc9W3ZZ8XPVgQlQx7ggvLgW3f9gfp3j0KrqW1BbVW91wqxT3W2nLWlm3QD2sKW7hWc-76WC2z6VGNdnG3zv1xCW1y6mR47jbmjwW2HYYBL39vn69W7Bj7pr1mdpFrW7BMqxZ15_q3GW1GqBpP5Bg1ZBW3T6VRL4bjLJqW1C-PKN49wCsZW6Pt04q6T27Z6dGNm7l04 ) (Wednesday) as two visual pros show how to turn a basic build into something that feels premium, all inside Bolt. Laurel Beyers (designer + UX consultant) and Clark Wimberly (design engineer + agency owner) will answer your questions and explain a ton of practical ways to sharpen your site’s design: - Smart planning and UX strategy that actually saves time - How to use prompts to nail your aesthetic faster - Adding fonts, icons, and polish that make clients go “woah” You’ll definitely walk away with something you hadn’t thought of before…personally, we can’t wait. RSVP now → (https://d5llC804.na1.hubspotlinks.com/Ctc/DQ+113/d5llC804/VWxdHS4xy-PzW7kM6n98JTlVRW3X6sTS5DF8KNN6WXHYv5fr76W50kH_H6lZ3mjW2H8Xwh2plQSVW7PqPyx8sr2b3W5lnHxN7H3BXGW2DJcQB2GjNR3VpC7yf4CW3L_W3q5yqM8YNV9KVfs6Yc4X0TcNW7NlLMP1XYqS8DS3q-2PZdDW4BQ_t15G42HSW9f7c4W5VCyv5W31mQhB2C2mBRW8khc1D2Pzk2-VLbRhZ41GBSDW1HftPy4MCc4jW2v-plJ3CL4JRW7tVSWS72JrQtW6z0vjh5G8ZjTV4086F9hgypWW8n3zB26v_QQFW8hPJ4v16ZwGZW36_Q2v8CY3ZkW1s6RsQ3QC7WdW3XxnCm95LGfTW6BnfCb3JsbdnW12tW626Sg8wRW34dTG093YCZHW4pnf0h59FVkPW31w-G65cZ_r0TtVBK3XH9djW31fBH75w8VrxW4Y6QK38pSfRvf33jMSl04 ) Connect your existing Supa... [truncated]','ericsimons@stackblitz.com','E