 contain confidential or privileged information. If you are not the intended recipient, any dissemination, use, review, distribution, printing or copying of the information contained in this e-mail message and/or attachments to it are strictly prohibited. If you have received this communication in error, please notify us by reply e-mail or telephone and immediately and permanently delete the message and any attachments. Thank you','careers@tcs.com','EMAIL','CLOSED','TKT-1769593393937','Manoj Iyer (EMAIL)','Email Support Team','EMAIL','2026-01-28 13:30:24.837140',0.9,_binary '','HIGH','OUTLOOK','AI','2026-01-29 06:22:52.566480',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Email configuration issue has been resolved. Updated SMTP server settings in Outlook to mail.powergrid.com on port 587 with TLS encryption. Also cleared the email cache and reconfigured the mailbox sync settings. User can now send and receive emails successfully.','ENGINEER_RESOLVED',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'=== AI VERIFICATION REPORT ===\nVerification Time: 2026-01-29T11:52:52.565423700\nQuality Score: 100/100\n\n',100,'VERIFIED','2026-01-29 06:22:52.566480',NULL,NULL,NULL),(12,'2026-01-28 02:59:18.000000','Help shape MongoDB Atlas in 2026','MONGODB','We\'re planning for 2026 and we want your input. Plus: 3 skills every MongoDB developer needs this year.  Hi HARINI, I wanted to send a quick note to thank you for building with MongoDB Atlas in 2025. Last year, tens of thousands of customers and millions of developers depended on MongoDB’s modern data platform for their most mission-critical workloads. We have big plans for 2026, and we want you to help drive them: What should MongoDB Atlas prioritize in 2026? If there’s anything we can build or improve - new features, smoother workflows, or small fixes - that would help you work faster and better serve your customers, share your feedback below or just reply to this email. Submit feedback    I also wanted to share three things I believe every MongoDB developer should know going into 2026: * Diagnosing query performance: The most important skill you can master this year is diagnosing and remediating slow queries. Make sure you’re comfortable using our diagnostictools  and workflows  for slow queries, andrefining your application’s data model . * Connecting your AI tools to MongoDB via MCP: Our local MCP server  allows you to manage infrastructure configuration and provide cluster and data context to your AI coding tools. As models improve and AI tooling standards develop, it’s important to provide your AI tools with this context as they write code that interacts with MongoDB. * Getting free support on Atlas: Every Atlas organization includes free Basic Support via chat Monday through Friday. For deeper technical help, our Developer Support tier offers performance optimization and expert advice to help you tune your environment. You don’t need to wait for things to break to get help. Activate your free30-day trial  if you haven’t already, oropen a case  . Our mission remains the same: to help you unleash the power of software and data. I\'m looking forward to hearing from you! Thanks for building with us, and here’s to a great 2026. - Charlie { name : \"Charlie Xu\", tit... [truncated]','mongodb@team.mongodb.com','EMAIL','ASSIGNED','TKT-1769593442955','Amit Kumar (NET)','Application Support Team','SOFTWARE','2026-01-28 13:31:12.966359',0.9,_binary '','CRITICAL','PERFORMANCE',NULL,NULL,'2026-01-29 04:43:29.969566','SLA Breach - Level 3 - Department Head escalation. Priority: CRITICAL, SLA: 2 hours, Overtime: 23.7 hours (1287% of SLA)',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'LEVEL_3','2026-04-02 17:36:33.691664','Neha Gupta (APP)','2026-01-29 04:43:29.969566',_binary '','2026-01-28 04:59:18.000000',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(13,'2026-01-28 09:55:00.116651',NULL,'EMP001','My laptop is not connecting to WiFi network',NULL,'CHATBOT','ASSIGNED','TKT-1769594100162','Anita Joshi (HW)','Network Team','NETWORK','2026-01-28